que qui refondera la justice pour l’ensemble des trois Amériques au moment même où les conséquences du réchauffement climatique atteignent le point de non-retour.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aFrench-Canadian dramaxIndian authorsxHistory and criticism. 0aIndian theaterzQuébec (Province)xHistory and criticism. 0aIndians in literature. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / General.2bisacsh1 aDurand, Yves Sioui, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311127253508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020z978311127473740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763748610423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763748610/original  a978-3-11-127253-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-127473-7  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles